title: Taylor Swift & The Number 13
description:
We all know Taylor Swift's lucky number is 13, but did you know she's been subtly hiding the number as easter eggs throughout her entire discography? Find out some of the best moments Taylor has used 13 and why we decided to name this podcast after her iconic number!
